    <item>
      <title>特朗普会在税收谈判中与参议院金融小组会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-to-meet-with-senate-finance-panel-as-tax-talks-heat-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士说，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）计划与参议院财政委员会的共和党成员会面，负责制定数万亿税削减法案的小组国会的目标是今年通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-to-meet-with-senate-finance-panel-as-tax-talks-heat-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 15:38:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院民主党人在政治上有约束力，因为共和党人敢于美国关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/senate-democrats-wobble-as-republicans-dare-them-on-us-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党人在11月大选失败并无助地看着埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）拆除联邦政府后，在华盛顿拥有罕见的杠杆作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/senate-democrats-wobble-as-republicans-dare-them-on-us-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 14:48:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orban将减税量扩大以关闭挑战者在匈牙利的领导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/hungary-s-orban-slightly-narrows-challenger-magyar-s-poll-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）为母亲提供了终生的终身所得税免税，以缩小挑战者在大众支持方面的领先优势，在下次选举之前还有一年多的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/hungary-s-orban-slightly-narrows-challenger-magyar-s-poll-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:59:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京可能会拖出乌克兰休战谈判来寻求条款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/putin-eyes-way-to-agree-to-truce-terms-with-his-own-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）可能会同意与乌克兰的最终休战条件，但希望自己的条件事先达到，可能会拖延谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/putin-eyes-way-to-agree-to-truce-terms-with-his-own-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大在贸易战中与美国钢铁，铝的关税袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/canada-to-unveil-retaliatory-tariffs-on-21-billion-of-us-goods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大在特朗普政府继续对这两种材料进口的全球进口征税后，宣布了包括钢铁和铝制产品在内的约300亿加元（208亿美元）的美国制造产品的新25％关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/canada-to-unveil-retaliatory-tariffs-on-21-billion-of-us-goods</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普金属关税火花报复动作，呼吁进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-take-effect-with-no-exemptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对钢铁和铝进口的25％关税周三生效，引起了亚洲出口统治的关注，并且随着全球贸易战争进入岩石阶段，欧盟和加拿大的立即报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/trump-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-take-effect-with-no-exemptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 04:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储员工在1月会见了财政部的总督团队，备案节目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/fed-staff-met-with-treasury-s-doge-team-in-january-filing-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新法庭文件，美联储的工作人员与财政部合作，使埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的政府效率访问联邦支付系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/fed-staff-met-with-treasury-s-doge-team-in-january-filing-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 23:11:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官在特朗普的命令中否认贿赂案的延迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/judge-denies-long-delay-of-bribery-case-in-test-of-trump-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位联邦法官说，在唐纳德·特朗普总统的命令下命令执行《外国腐败行为法》之后，他将不允许长时间延迟贿赂审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/judge-denies-long-delay-of-bribery-case-in-test-of-trump-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 21:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国际开发署官方命令工作人员销毁机密文件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/usaid-official-orders-staff-to-destroy-classified-documents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一名高级官员的备忘录，美国国际开发署的一些工作人员被勒令销毁机密的文件和人事记录，此举引起了新的法律挑战，但后来被描述为常规的政府官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/usaid-official-orders-staff-to-destroy-classified-documents</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 19:09:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
